data.description: Charming three bedroom home in Peru School District. Situated on 1.70 acres with a beautiful and private 24' round in-ground pool with brand new liner. This home also has a massive detached shop with 10' and 12' doors and a second floor loft. Detached 2-car garage has storage loft as well as a whole house generator. Inside you'll find hardwood floors, updated appliances and many other upgrades!
